      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions must be reproduced in simulation with documented uncertainty on inlet/outlet conditions.",
      "rationale": "Inlet flow waveform from FDA experiments was approximated as steady-state; pulsatile effects were not captured. Uncertainty on inlet conditions was estimated from literature rather than measured. Achieved level 2 falls well below required level 4."
