      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All uncertain model inputs must be characterised with probability distributions derived from measurements or literature with documented justification.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo sampling was performed on three inputs (viscosity, speed, inlet flow). Material properties for blood rheology were taken from a single literature source without uncertainty characterisation. Achieved level 2."
