      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample size and variability must be documented; statistical power of validation dataset must be assessed.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark data sample size and inter-sample variability were not documented in the assessment. No statistical power analysis was performed. Achieved level 1."
