    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors were not assessed and represent epistemic gaps. The mesh-independence verification activity (MRL5-MESH-VERIF) was conducted and documented in the assessment narrative, and its outputs are referenced throughout the validation discussion. The overall credibility package is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission with the understanding that the documented gaps will be addressed in the next development cycle. The decision is formally recorded as Accepted for submission purposes pending gap closure commitments.",
